modules.description: This module enables programmatic construction and transformation of OCaml AST nodes for RPC systems, focusing on generating server/client wrappers, function parameters, and caching mechanisms. It operates on abstract syntax trees from `Astlib.Ast_500.Parsetree` and `Ppxlib.Ast`, supporting tasks like tuple creation, pattern matching, and configuration-driven code generation. It is particularly useful for automating boilerplate in distributed systems where type-safe remote calls and data serialization are required.
